{
  "stem": "13395.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you're marching in a column there, and they give you the shovel, and you are-- they're walking with the dogs, and you don't dare to even look up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one day, we hear the planes overhead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we look up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It looks like it's snowing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as it comes closer down, we realized these were flyers, pieces of paper.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Immediately, the orders from the guards that if you dared to pick one up, they shoot you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, they cannot control 1,000 women and all the paper that was come down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As one piece of paper came close by me, I put a shovel of dirt on top of it and continued working.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when I picked it up later and took it to camp and read it, it was a message for us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Hold on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We are coming to liberate you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I can only think of the pilot who flew over enemy territory to give us the greatest gift of all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He gave us hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was no hope, but he gave us hope.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Hold on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know if he returned safely home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I'll always be grateful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "On May 9, 8, they called us out again for an assembly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we got a whole speech that, yes, the war is coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And yes, the allied are winning the war, but that doesn't mean that we will be free, because the camp is rigged with dynamite, and they will blow us up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the camp is being blown up before the allied marched, march in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we should not celebrate yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
